              &lt;div class=&quot;d-inline-flex ai-center&quot;&gt;
&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;/users/901641/artofwarfare&quot; title=&quot;19,300 reputation&quot; class=&quot;comment-user&quot;&gt;ArtOfWarfare&lt;/a&gt;
                &lt;/div&gt;
                &lt;span class=&quot;comment-date&quot; dir=&quot;ltr&quot;&gt;&lt;a class=&quot;comment-link&quot; href=&quot;#comment53336476_18979314&quot;&gt;&lt;span title=&quot;2015-09-23 19:28:07Z, License: CC BY-SA 3.0&quot; class=&quot;relativetime-clean&quot;&gt;Sep 23, 2015 at 19:28&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
            &lt;/div&gt;

            &lt;div class=&quot;comment-body js-comment-edit-hide&quot;&gt;

                &lt;span class=&quot;comment-copy&quot;&gt;@ArtOfWarfare, you can use &lt;code&gt;__all__ = [...]&lt;/code&gt; to limit what gets imported with &lt;code&gt;import *&lt;/code&gt;. But aside from that, yes, you&apos;re left with a messy top-level namespace.&lt;/span&gt;

              &lt;div class=&quot;d-inline-flex ai-center&quot;&gt;
&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;/users/2147440/nathan-gould&quot; title=&quot;7,395 reputation&quot; class=&quot;comment-user&quot;&gt;Nathan Gould&lt;/a&gt;
                &lt;/div&gt;
                &lt;span class=&quot;comment-date&quot; dir=&quot;ltr&quot;&gt;&lt;a class=&quot;comment-link&quot; href=&quot;#comment53342747_18979314&quot;&gt;&lt;span title=&quot;2015-09-23 23:28:09Z, License: CC BY-SA 3.0&quot; class=&quot;relativetime-clean&quot;&gt;Sep 23, 2015 at 23:28&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
            &lt;/div&gt;

            &lt;div class=&quot;comment-body js-comment-edit-hide&quot;&gt;

                &lt;span class=&quot;comment-copy&quot;&gt;@NathanGould you could also use single leading underscore variables which are not imported by &lt;code&gt;import *&lt;/code&gt; by default. Eg: &lt;code&gt;import os as _os&lt;/code&gt; and use &lt;code&gt;_os&lt;/code&gt; inside the &lt;code&gt;__init__.py&lt;/code&gt; module in place of &lt;code&gt;os&lt;/code&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;

              &lt;div class=&quot;d-inline-flex ai-center&quot;&gt;
&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;/users/3922534/mathieu-rollet&quot; title=&quot;1,561 reputation&quot; class=&quot;comment-user&quot;&gt;Mathieu Rollet&lt;/a&gt;
                &lt;/div&gt;
